
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Orange Atlas Practice Hub</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/orange-atlas/assets/orangeAtlas.png" type="image/png">
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Source+Serif+4:opsz,wght@8..60,600;8..60,700&display=swap");

    :root {
      --bg: #070b13;
      --bg-alt: #0c1320;
      --panel: #111a2b;
      --panel-soft: #172235;
      --line: rgba(174, 196, 229, 0.2);
      --text: #e8f0ff;
      --muted: #9aadcb;
      --brand: #ff8f3f;
      --teal: #4bc3b1;
      --ok: #74e3d3;
      --shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(4, 8, 15, 0.62);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(170deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg-alt) 52%, #0a111d 100%);
      padding: 1.35rem 1.1rem 3rem;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    body::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(75, 195, 177, 0.1), transparent 30%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.1), transparent 30%);
        animation: move-glow 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      background: rgba(17, 26, 43, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      animation: fade-up 0.55s ease both;
      position: sticky;
      top: 1rem;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.72rem;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 0.65rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.46);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.22);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      animation: spin 10s linear infinite;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      margin-top: 0.08rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .status {
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: #ffd1a8;
      background: rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.35);
      padding: 0.28rem 0.62rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fade-up 0.62s ease both;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: "Source Serif 4", serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--brand), var(--teal), var(--brand));
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: text-focus-in 1s cubic-bezier(0.550, 0.085, 0.680, 0.530) both, animated-gradient 5s ease infinite;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: #afc0dc;
      line-height: 1.72;
      max-width: 60ch;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      animation: slide-in 1s ease 0.2s both;
    }
    
    .hero .cta {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--brand), #ff7f2f);
        color: var(--bg);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        animation: fade-up 1s ease 0.4s both, pulse 2.5s infinite 1s;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.2);
    }

    .hero .cta:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.4);
    }
    
    .section-title {
        font-family: "Source Serif 4", serif;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin: 4rem 0 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        animation: fade-up 0.74s ease both;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
        background: var(--panel-soft);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 0.95rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        animation: fade-up 0.8s ease both;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--teal);
    }
    
    .feature-title {
        font-family: "Source Serif 4", serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .feature-description {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .course-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .course-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 0.95rem;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--panel) 0%, var(--panel-soft) 100%);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      animation: fade-up 0.62s ease both;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .course-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.1), transparent 40%);
        transform: rotate(0deg);
        transition: transform 1s ease-in-out;
    }
    
    .course-card:hover::before {
        transform: rotate(360deg);
    }

    .course-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .course-card.live {
      border-color: rgba(75, 195, 177, 0.5);
    }

    .course-card.locked {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .chip {
      width: fit-content;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .chip.live {
      color: #93f8e8;
      background: rgba(75, 195, 177, 0.16);
      border-color: rgba(75, 195, 177, 0.42);
    }

    .chip.locked {
      color: #ffd3ab;
      background: rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.15);
      border-color: rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.38);
    }

    .course-name {
      font-family: "Source Serif 4", serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .course-meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .course-cta {
        margin-top: auto;
        color: var(--teal);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fade-up 0.82s ease both;
    }

    @keyframes fade-up {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    
    @keyframes slide-in {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }
    
    @keyframes spin {
        from {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        to {
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }
    
    @keyframes move-glow {
        0%, 100% {
            transform: translateX(0) translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateX(40px) translateY(20px);
        }
    }
    
    @keyframes animated-gradient {
        0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    @keyframes text-focus-in {
      0% {
        -webkit-filter: blur(12px);
                filter: blur(12px);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      100% {
        -webkit-filter: blur(0px);
                filter: blur(0px);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
        0% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.3); }
        50% { transform: scale(1.08); box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.4); }
        100% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 143, 63, 0.3); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .course-grid, .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      body {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 4rem 1rem;
      }
      
      .hero h1 {
          font-size: 2.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <header class="topbar" aria-label="Site header">
      <div class="brand">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/orange-atlas/assets/orangeAtlas.png" alt="Orange Atlas logo">
        <div>
          <p class="brand-name">Orange Atlas</p>
          <p class="brand-sub">Practice Test Hub</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="status">Academic Portal</span>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Master Your Skills</h1>
      <p>Your one-stop destination for mastering new concepts. Explore our courses and start your learning journey today.</p>
      <a href="#courses" class="cta">Explore Courses</a>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features-grid" aria-label="Platform Features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Targeted Practice</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">Focus on specific units to improve your skills where you need it most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Instant Feedback</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">Track your progress and learn from your mistakes with immediate results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4.5 12.5l3-3a7 7 0 0 1 10 0l3 3"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M5 12v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Aligned Content</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">Practice with materials that are directly aligned with your course curriculum.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <h2 id="courses" class="section-title">Available Courses</h2>
    <section class="course-grid" aria-label="Available courses">
      <a class="course-card live" href="./spanish2/">
        <span class="chip live">Active</span>
        <h3 class="course-name">Spanish 2</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Practice hub with unit-based Senderos exams plus dedicated grammar collections for targeted review.</p>
        <p class="course-cta">Open Course Hub -></p>
      </a>

      <div class="course-card locked" aria-disabled="true">
        <span class="chip locked">Coming Soon</span>
        <h3 class="course-name">Spanish 1</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Foundation vocabulary, present tense, and early conversation assessments.</p>
        <p class="course-cta">Course shell ready</p>
      </div>

      <div class="course-card locked" aria-disabled="true">
        <span class="chip locked">Coming Soon</span>
        <h3 class="course-name">AP Spanish Language</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Interpretive and presentational practice sets aligned to AP tasks.</p>
        <p class="course-cta">Course shell ready</p>
      </div>

      <div class="course-card locked" aria-disabled="true">
        <span class="chip locked">Coming Soon</span>
        <h3 class="course-name">French 1</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Reserved slot for expansion into additional language pathways.</p>
        <p class|="course-cta">Course shell ready</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="footer-note">
      Structure standard: keep course homes at `/<course>/` and store legacy tests in unit folders inside each course.
    </p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
